            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "In the centre of a quiet town, a tower appeared and captured all of the town’s residents within it. In ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Lonesome Village",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ", you control Wes the Coyote as he works to save the villagers from the tower. Brought to us by Ogre Pixel, ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Lonesome Village",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " is a mix of puzzle and life-simulator games where you solve puzzles to free villagers and ascend the tower; build friendships, and solve villagers’ needs and issues within the town to help rebuild their homes.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
