            "text": " boasts a cutesy, cartoonish art-style that favours large eyes and no mouths. The characters within the game are unique, the game is colourful and inviting, and all-in-all, it’s a pleasant visual experience. The main character Wes has a great design, and one that I wouldn’t mind owning a plushie of if one were available... Oh wait, ",
