          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " also boasts a robust suite of challenging puzzles to overcome. Each floor of the tower offers a unique puzzle, which becomes harder as you ascend. I personally did not come across a puzzle that I got stuck on, but neither did I come across a puzzle I felt was easier than the one prior to it. A healthy amount of challenge without reaching the point of frustration is a delicate balance to achieve, and it is one I feel ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
